<A>__{traveling shot. plato. he is coming up the walk to his house. when plato has come a few feet, somebody whistles. plato and camera stop. short, quiet whistles come from the boxwood and shrubbery on both sides of the walk. plato turns and starts to run, camera following. he gets to his door, tries the key, but in his panic it will not go into the lock. suddenly a hand reaches in and jerks him around. crunch stands above him. goon closes in from the other side. all very tense and hotted up!}
